thread.title_full: Motiva Port Arthur refinery suffered fire in a catalytic reformer - sources | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Motiva Port Arthur refinery suffered fire in a catalytic reformer - sources
text:
HOUSTON, July 29 Motiva Enterprises LLC's Port Arthur, Texas refinery suffered a small fire on Wednesday in a catalytic reformer, sources told Reuters.
There were no injuries and production was not impacted, they added.
A reformer converts refining byproducts into additives for gasoline and can produce some gasoline itself. (Reporting By Erwin Seba)
